OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FState of emergency in      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FCatalonia over worst ever  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fdrought                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Spanish region of Catalonia has    
OL,6, declared a state of emergency as it    
OL,7, faces its worst drought on record.     
OL,9,FFrom Thursday residents will be banned 
OL,10,Ffrom washing their cars and filling up 
OL,11,Fempty swimming pools under a measures  
OL,12,Fbrought in to tackle the crisis.       
OL,14,FMore than six million Catalans will be 
OL,15,Faffected across 200 towns and cities,  
OL,16,Fincluding the capital Barcelona.       
OL,18,FThe restrictions were announced after  
OL,19,Freservoirs fell to close to 16% of     
OL,20,Ftheir capacity.                        
